                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150215-113-off669 t18150215-113-cd670"></join>, a great coat, value 1 l. a pair of breeches, value 5 s. a pair of gaiters, value 5 s. and two handkerchiefs, value 1 s. and seven shillings and six pence in monies numbered, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18150215-113-victim960" type="victimName">
